This is a Qobuz plugin for XBMC
-------------------------------
The goal is to integrate access to the great Qobuz library directly from XBMC.

Main Features : 
---------------

- Show playlist already filled using the standard players (web, desktop)
- Show purchased products
- Show recommended albums by genre and type  
- Search by track name, album name and artist name
- Integrate with xbmc gapless play
- Support flac or mp3 play (using settings)
- 

Configuration:
--------------

- Enter valid Qobuz credentials using addon settings, 
note: you need Hifi subscription to stream flac files and premium subscription to play mp3
get yours here : http://www.qobuz.com/abonnement-streaming

 
